> This breaks for filenames with spaces.<p>Useful things in bash:<p><pre><code>  export IFS=$&#x27;
&#x27;
</code></pre>
or<p><pre><code>  export IFS=$&#x27;
&#x27;
  for I in `$COMMAND` do
    $OTHER_COMMAND &quot;${I}&quot;
  done
</code></pre>
or, generally:<p><pre><code>  find ./ -print0 | xargs -0 $COMMAND</code></pre>
